Class BiomeAccessHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.legacy.structure_gel.access_helpers.BiomeAccessHelper

  • public class BiomeAccessHelper
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains methods to add various things to biomes, such as features, structures, carvers, mob spawns, etc. Thanks 1.16.2.

    David
